<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ:</span> قَتَادَةُ: <span class="c2">«إِنْ كَانَ مَاءً دَافِقًا اغْتَسَلَ»</span> فَقُلْتُ لِقَتَادَةَ: كَيْفَ يَعْلَمُ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«بِشَمِّهِ»</span>،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ الْحَكَمُ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَا يَغْتَسِلُ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>